data.name: customSqlQuery1.Sql
data.value: SELECT ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY ds.MaDauSach) AS STT, ds.MaDauSach, ds.TenDauSach, ds.SoLuongTong AS SoLuongTong, ISNULL(CoSan.SoLuongCoSan, 0) AS CoSan, (ds.SoLuongTong - ISNULL(CoSan.SoLuongCoSan, 0)) AS DangMuon -- Tính = Tổng - Có sẵn FROM DAUSACH ds LEFT JOIN ( -- Sách có sẵn (tình trạng = 1) SELECT s.MaDauSach, COUNT(*) AS SoLuongCoSan FROM SACH s WHERE s.MaTinhTrang = 1 GROUP BY s.MaDauSach ) CoSan ON ds.MaDauSach = CoSan.MaDauSach WHERE ds.TrangThai = 1 ORDER BY ds.MaDauSach;
